      "width": 1400,
      "height": 120,
      "color": "1",
      "text": "# 🏗️ 抖音视频流水线 — 架构洞察白板\n**Pipeline V2: Skill+Script 混合编排** · AI判断 + 脚本执行 · 延时并发 · 状态机驱动"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "legend",
      "x": 600,
      "y": -1600,
      "width": 500,
      "height": 280,
      "color": "6",
      "text": "## 📖 图例\n\n| 色 | 含义 |\n|---|---|\n| 🟥 红 | 核心流程/高风险 |\n| 🟧 橙 | 异步/警告 |\n| 🟨 黄 | 外部依赖 |\n| 🟩 绿 | 持久化数据 |\n| 🟦 蓝 | AI/Skill |\n| 🟪 紫 | 设计决策 |\n\n**🔗 点击 file 节点 → 跳转详细白板**\n\n---\n**📁 白板定位**:\n- 本白板: 整体架构\n- content-cleaner-flow: AI整理流程\n- stage1/2/4: 各阶段详情"
    },
    {
      "type": "group",
      "id": "group-dna",
      "x": -2200,
      "y": -1400,
      "width": 1400,
      "height": 1000,
      "color": "6",
      "label": "🧬 架构 DNA — 设计哲学"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "dna-philosophy",
      "x": -2160,
      "y": -1340,
      "width": 1320,
      "height": 420,
      "color": "6",
      "text": "## 🎯 核心设计哲学\n\n### 1. Skill+Script 混合编排\n**AI 做判断，脚本做执行**\n- 🤖 Skill: 需要语义理解的环节（质量评估/内容整理/关键词优化）\n- 📜 Script: 确定性操作（下载/转录/验证/分发/归档）\n- 🔄 交接点: Skill 输出 → Script 验证路由\n\n### 2. 单一真相源 (Single Source of Truth)\n**videos.json 是状态机的唯一驱动者**\n- 所有组件通过 status 字段协调\n- metadata.json 不存状态，仅存快照\n- 归档文件参与去重，但不参与状态流转\n\n### 3. 渐进精炼 (Progressive Refinement)\n**原始数据 → 结构化元数据 → AI分析内容 → 分发输出**\n- 每个阶段只做一件事，做到极致\n- 错误影响范围被批次参数限制"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "dna-pattern",
      "x": -2160,
      "y": -880,
      "width": 640,
      "height": 420,
      "color": "6",
      "text": "## 🧩 架构模式识别\n\n**管道模式 (Pipeline)**\nStage1→2→4→Cleaner→Validate→Distribute\n每阶段输入/输出明确，可独立执行\n\n**状态机模式 (FSM)**\npending→downloading→downloaded→\ntranscribed→processed|insufficient\n状态驱动，异常可回退\n\n**路由器模式 (Router)**\nvalidate-cleaned 是唯一路由器\naccessible→distribute\ninsufficient→review\n失败→回退重试\n\n**观察者模式 (Observer)**\nconsistency-check 独立验证\n不参与主流程，事后审计"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "dna-antipattern",
      "x": -1480,
      "y": -880,
      "width": 640,
      "height": 420,
      "color": "1",
      "text": "## ⚠️ 反模式警示\n\n**🔴 上帝文件 (God File)**\nvideos.json 承载过多职责:\n- 状态机驱动\n- 去重索引\n- 归档触发\n→ 单点故障，损坏影响全局\n\n**✅ 硬编码蔓延 (已修复)**\n所有脚本统一从 _shared/config.js 导入路径\n修复时间: 2026-04-24\n\n**✅ 双状态文件 (已修复)**\n删除遗留的 state/ 目录\n修复时间: 2026-04-24\n\n**🟡 类型逃逸**\ncategory: string|null 实际存储多值\n→ 下游需 split 解析，类型契约失效"
    },
    {
      "type": "group",
      "id": "group-pipeline",
      "x": -700,
      "y": -1400,
      "width": 3000,
      "height": 1000,
      "color": "1",
      "label": "🔄 核心流水线 — 数据流与控制流"
    },
    {
      "type": "file",
      "id": "stage1-file",
      "x": -660,
      "y": -1320,
      "width": 440,
      "height": 300,
      "color": "3",
      "file": "architecture-canvas/stage1-architecture.canvas"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "stage1-detail",
      "x": -660,
      "y": -980,
      "width": 440,
      "height": 220,
      "color": "3",
      "text": "## Stage1 博主发现 📜\n\n**输入**: search-keywords.json + blacklist\n**核心**: 关键词搜索 → 博主质量评分 → 相关性分析\n**输出**: bloggers.json\n**关键参数**: min_score=40, min_followers=1000\n**复杂度**: 🟡 Medium — API依赖+评分逻辑"
    },
    {
      "type": "file",
      "id": "stage2-file",
      "x": -160,
      "y": -1320,
      "width": 440,
      "height": 300,
      "color": "3",
      "file": "architecture-canvas/stage2-video-collect.canvas"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "stage2-detail",
      "x": -160,
      "y": -980,
      "width": 440,
      "height": 220,
      "color": "3",
      "text": "## Stage2 视频采集 📜\n\n**输入**: bloggers.json\n**核心**: 遍历博主 → 获取视频列表 → 去重 → 相关性筛选\n**输出**: videos.json(7字段) + metadata.json\n**关键**: author_id 匹配 ⚠️ (链路断裂风险)\n**复杂度**: 🟡 Medium — 去重+归档感知"
    },
    {
      "type": "file",
      "id": "stage4-file",
      "x": 340,
      "y": -1320,
      "width": 440,
      "height": 300,
      "color": "4",
      "file": "architecture-canvas/stage4-architecture.canvas"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "stage4-detail",
      "x": 340,
      "y": -980,
      "width": 440,
      "height": 220,
      "color": "4",
      "text": "## Stage4 下载+转录 📜\n\n**输入**: videos.json (status=pending)\n**核心**: 音频下载 → Whisper转录 → 状态更新\n**输出**: audio/{id}.mp3 + transcripts/{id}.txt\n**关键**: 延时并发 batch_download=2\n**复杂度**: 🔴 High — GPU资源+进程管理\n\n### 🎯 智能模型选择\n| 视频数量 | 模型 | 说明 |\n|----------|------|------|\n| ≤2 | ggml-small | 高精度 |\n| 3-50 | ggml-base | 平衡 |\n| >50 | ggml-tiny | 高速度 |\n\n**手动指定**: `--whisper_model small`"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "cleaner-node",
      "x": 840,
      "y": -1320,
      "width": 440,
      "height": 300,
      "color": "5",
      "text": "## 🤖 Content-Cleaner\nAI Agent Skill\n\n**输入**: transcripts/{id}.txt + videos.json\n**核心变换**:\n1. 质量判断 → accessible / insufficient\n2. 文本优化 → 纠错/去噪/重组\n3. 内容分析 → keywords\n\n**输出**: cleaned-results/{id}.json\n- accessible: 5字段 (main_content≥300字)\n- insufficient: 4字段 (reason必填)\n\n**三不原则**: 不虚构/不损毁/不脱脸"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "cleaner-detail",
      "x": 840,
      "y": -980,
      "width": 440,
      "height": 220,
      "color": "5",
      "text": "## Content-Cleaner 深度 🤖\n\n**执行序列**:\n环境扫描 → 深度读取 → 内在思考 → 单文件写入 → 强制验证 → 状态回执\n\n**质量门控**:\n- 去重压缩比 ≥ 0.3\n- 原始压缩比 ≤ 1.5\n- 中文引号用「」\n\n**复杂度**: 🔴 Critical — AI输出不确定性\n**风险**: 幻觉/遗漏/格式偏差"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "validate-node",
      "x": 1340,
      "y": -1320,
      "width": 440,
      "height": 300,
      "color": "2",
      "text": "## ✅ validate-cleaned.js\n唯一路由器 📜\n\n**验证项**:\n- cleaned-results/ 文件数=1\n- videos.json 存在 video_id\n- 基础字段完整(3)\n- accessible: main_content≥300 + 压缩比\n- insufficient: reason 非空\n\n**路由决策**:\n✅ accessible+通过 → distribute\n✅ insufficient+通过 → review-handler\n❌ 任何失败 → 重置 status=transcribed\n\n**复杂度**: 🟡 Medium — 路由逻辑"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "distribute-node",
      "x": 1840,
      "y": -1320,
      "width": 400,
      "height": 260,
      "color": "4",
      "text": "## 📤 distribute-cleaned.js 📜\n\n**4个写入目标**:\n1. results/{博主}/videos/{id}.json\n2. results/{博主}/metadata.json\n   (last_analyzed_at更新)\n3. data/discovered-keywords.json\n4. data/videos.json → status=processed\n\n**关键**: 三级回退匹配博主目录\n**复杂度**: 🟡 Medium"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "review-node",
      "x": 1840,
      "y": -1020,
      "width": 400,
      "height": 260,
      "color": "2",
      "text": "## 🔍 review-handler.js 📜\n\n**处理 insufficient**:\n- reason → 分类映射\n- 移动转录 → review/{类别}/\n- 追加追溯信息(URL/博主/原因)\n- status → insufficient\n- 清理临时文件 ⚠️\n\n**风险**: 临时文件泄漏\n**复杂度**: 🟢 Low"
    },
    {
      "type": "group",
      "id": "group-data",
      "x": -2200,
      "y": -300,
      "width": 4500,
      "height": 600,
      "color": "4",
      "label": "📄 数据层 — 持久化存储 & 生命周期"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "videos-hub",
      "x": -2160,
      "y": -220,
      "width": 600,
      "height": 460,
      "color": "1",
      "text": "## 🏛️ videos.json\n单一真相源 · 状态机驱动\n\n**核心字段**: aweme_id/url/author/author_id/sec_uid/status/quality\n\n**写入者** (5个):\n- Stage2: 创建(7字段)\n- Stage4: status→downloaded\n- Stage4-transcribe: status→transcribed\n- distribute: status→processed\n- review: status→insufficient\n\n**归档**: 终态→videos-archive-{YYYY-MM}.json\n**当前**: 归档138个 + 活跃31个\n\n✅ 已修复: 原子写入(先写临时文件再rename)\n防止并发写入导致文件损坏"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "bloggers-file",
      "x": -1480,
      "y": -220,
      "width": 480,
      "height": 300,
      "color": "4",
      "text": "## bloggers.json\n博主轻量索引\n\n**5字段**: sec_uid/name/author_id/url/status\n\n**写入**: Stage1, Stage2\n**读取**: Stage2, Stage4, distribute\n\n⚠️ author_id 可能为空\n→ Stage4 过滤失败"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "metadata-file",
      "x": -940,
      "y": -220,
      "width": 500,
      "height": 300,
      "color": "4",
      "text": "## metadata.json\n博主详情+视频快照\n\n`results/{博主名}_{secUid前10位}/`\n\n**博主**: follower_count/likes_count/video_count/douyin_id/ip_location/score\n**视频列表**: videos[] 每个视频15+字段\n**质量统计**: total_videos/high_quality_count/inaccessible_count\n**博主定位**: category(领域), summary(一句话定位)\n\n**写入**: Stage1, Stage2, distribute(last_analyzed_at), consistency-check(统计), blogger-optimizer(category/summary仅null时)\n**不存状态** — 仅快照"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "transcript-lifecycle",
      "x": -380,
      "y": -220,
      "width": 560,
      "height": 460,
      "color": "4",
      "text": "## 📁 transcripts/ 生命周期\n\n```\n┌─ Whisper转录写入 ─────────┐\n│  transcripts/{id}.txt     │\n│         ↓                 │\n│  content-cleaner 读取     │\n│         ↓                 │\n│  validate 路由决策        │\n│    ┌────┴────┐            │\n│    ↓         ↓            │\n│ accessible  insufficient  │\n│    ↓         ↓            │\n│ archived/  review/{类}/  │\n│ {date}/    追加追溯信息   │\n└───────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n**归档**: archived/{date}/{id}.txt\n**审阅**: review/{类别}/{id}.txt\n\n### Review 问题分类\n| 目录 | 数量 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| content-fragmented | 8 | 转录过短/碎片化 |\n| whisper-hallucination | 3 | Whisper幻觉 |\n\n**读取**: blogger-optimizer（质量评估）"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "cleaned-dir",
      "x": 240,
      "y": -220,
      "width": 400,
      "height": 200,
      "color": "2",
      "text": "## 📁 cleaned-results/\n临时中转站\n\n`data/cleaned-results/{id}.json`\n\n**写入**: content-cleaner(AI)\n**读取**: validate-cleaned\n**生命周期**: 临时，验证后删除\n⚠️ 泄漏风险: updateVideosJson异常时"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "search-kw",
      "x": 240,
      "y": 40,
      "width": 400,
      "height": 200,
      "color": "3",
      "text": "## search-keywords.json\n搜索关键词索引\n\n- id/keyword/status\n- search_count/found_bloggers\n- quality_score/quality_level\n\n**写入**: Stage1\n**读取**: Stage1, keyword-optimizer\n**优化**: AI评估效果，筛选推荐词"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "discovered-kw",
      "x": 700,
      "y": -220,
      "width": 400,
      "height": 200,
      "color": "3",
      "text": "## discovered-keywords.json\n发现的关键词\n\n- keyword/source/discovered_at/status\n\n**写入**: Stage1, distribute\n**读取**: Stage1(关键词优化)\n\n**反馈环**: 内容分析发现新词 → 下轮搜索"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "blacklist-file",
      "x": 700,
      "y": 40,
      "width": 400,
      "height": 200,
      "color": "1",
      "text": "## blogger-blacklist.json\n黑名单（86个博主）\n\n- name/author_id/sec_uid\n- added_at/reason\n\n**脚本**: `scripts/utils/archive-blogger.js`\n**写入**: 手动/blogger-optimizer\n**读取**: Stage1(过滤)/blogger-optimizer\n\n**数据清理范围（10个文件）**:
| 文件 | 操作 |
|------|------|
| blogger-blacklist.json | 添加 |
| bloggers.json | 删除 |
| videos.json | 删除 |
| videos-index.json | 删除 |
| videos-exceptions.json | 删除 |
| videos-archive-*.json | 删除 |
| transcripts/archived/ | 删除 |
| transcripts/review/ | 删除 |
| active-bloggers-review-stats.json | 删除 |
| blogger-analysis.json | 删除 |\n\n**原因分类**:\n| 原因 | 数量 |\n|------|------|\n| 用户手动 | ~20 |\n| 质量为0% | ~10 |\n| 无新视频 | ~10 |\n| 内容不相关 | ~20 |\n| 无法访问 | ~5 |"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "archive-file",
      "x": 1160,
      "y": -220,
      "width": 500,
      "height": 300,
      "color": "4",
      "text": "## videos-archive-{YYYY-MM}.json\n终态视频归档 ✅\n\n**触发**: distribute/review写入终态后自动归档\n**内容**: processed/insufficient/inaccessible\n**读取**: loadAllAwemeIds() (Stage2去重)\n**写入**: archiveTerminalVideos()\n\n**归档感知**: validAwemeIds 含 videos.json + 所有归档文件\n→ 自动修复时不会误删归档视频"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "audio-dir",
      "x": 1720,
      "y": -220,
