    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "video-json-output",
      "x": 1720,
      "y": 40,
      "width": 500,
      "height": 200,
      "color": "4",
      "text": "## results/{博主}/videos/{id}.json\n最终输出 ✅\n\n**6必需**: video_id/url/author/analyzed_at/quality/main_content\n**2可选**: author_id/title\n\n**写入**: distribute-cleaned\n**这是流水线的最终产物**"
    },
    {
      "type": "group",
      "id": "group-status",
      "x": -2200,
      "y": 400,
      "width": 1600,
      "height": 600,
      "color": "2",
      "label": "📊 视频状态机 & Pipeline V2 编排"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "status-machine",
      "x": -2160,
      "y": 460,
      "width": 700,
      "height": 480,
      "color": "2",
      "text": "## 视频状态机 (FSM)\n\n```\n     ┌─────────── Stage2 ───────────┐\n     ↓                              │\n  pending ──Stage4──→ downloading   │\n     ↓                   ↓          │\n     │              downloaded       │\n     │                   ↓           │\n     │         Stage4-transcribe     │\n     │                   ↓           │\n     │             transcribed       │\n     │                   ↓           │\n     │         content-cleaner       │\n     │              ┌────┴────┐      │\n     ↓              ↓         ↓      │\n  failed      processed  insufficient│\n  (重试<3)    (终态✅)   (终态🔒)   │\n     ↓                              │\n  reset→pending                    │\n```\n\n**异常分支**: 任意→failed(重试<3次)\n**不可逆**: insufficient 终态\n**存储**: videos.json 唯一真相源"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "v2-flow",
      "x": -1400,
      "y": 460,
      "width": 740,
      "height": 480,
      "color": "1",
      "text": "## Pipeline V2 混合编排（已经遗弃的内容）\n\n```\n🤖 blogger-optimizer (Skill)\n    ↓\n🤖 keyword-optimizer (Skill) ← 博主<30时\n    ↓\n📜 stage1 (Script)\n    ↓\n📜 stage2 (Script)\n    ↓\n📜 consistency-check --fix (Script)\n    ↓\n┌──── 延时并发循环 ────┐             \n│ 📜 download 1-2个     │\n│ 📜 transcribe 1-2个   │\n│ 🤖 content-cleaner    │\n│ 📜 validate+distribute │\n│ ↓ 还有待处理? → 继续  │\n└──────────────────────┘\n```\n\n**命令**: `opencli douyin-videos pipeline-v2`\n**恢复**: `--from_stage stage2`"
    },
    {
      "type": "group",
      "id": "group-risks",
      "x": -500,
      "y": 400,
      "width": 2800,
      "height": 600,
      "color": "1",
      "label": "🔴 风险热力图 — 已识别架构风险"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "risk-critical",
      "x": -440,
      "y": 460,
      "width": 600,
      "height": 480,
      "color": "1",
      "text": "## 🔴 严重风险 (Critical)\n\n### 1. ✅ author_id 链路断裂 (已修复)\n**修复内容**:\n- Stage1: uid 为空时使用 null 而非空字符串\n- Stage2: 移除 blogger.author_id 兜底逻辑\n- Stage4: 增加 sec_uid 备选匹配\n\n**修复时间**: 2026-04-24\n\n### 2. ✅ videos.json 并发写入损坏 (已修复)\n**根因**: 多进程同时 writeFileSync\n**修复**: 原子写入(先写临时文件再rename)\n\n### 3. ✅ Stage4 转录进程管理 (已修复)\n**现状**: detectMaxConcurrency() + runConcurrent()\n**已实现**: GPU温度/显存自动调整 + 10s启动延迟\n**并发上限**: 最高3并发（温度≤60°C时）\n\n### 8. ✅ validate 路由器 (已修复)\n**修复内容**:\n- 增强 validate-cleaned.js 为完整路由器\n- accessible → distribute-cleaned.js\n- insufficient → review-handler.js\n- 失败 → 重置状态为 transcribed\n\n**修复时间**: 2026-04-24"
    },
